</br>21 Jehovah himself for the sake of his righteousness has taken a delight in that he should magnify the law and make it majestic.
</br>22 But it is a people plundered and pillaged, all of them being trapped in the holes, and in the houses of detention they have been kept hidden. They have come to be for plunder without a deliverer, for pillage without anyone to say: “Bring back!”
