</br>26 the One making the word of his servant come true, and the One that carries out completely the counsel of his own messengers; the One saying of Jerusalem, ‘She will be inhabited,’ and of the cities of Judah, ‘They will be rebuilt, and her desolated places I shall raise up’;
</br>27 the One saying to the watery deep, ‘Be evaporated; and all your rivers I shall dry up’;
